\{n_1,\ldots,n_k\}
m
m=n_1+\ldots+n_k
\mathcal{P}_m
x_1,\ldots,x_m
 \sum_{\pi\in\mathcal{P}_m}{c_\pi\; x_1^{r_1}}\cdot\ldots\cdot x_m^{r_m}  
 \sum_{r_1+\ldots+r_n=m}{\frac{m!}{r_1!\cdot\ldots\cdot r_n!}x_1^{r_1}\cdot\ldots\cdot x_n^{r_n}}=\left(x_1+\ldots+x_n\right)^m. 
y^m
 \sum_{\pi\in\mathcal{P}_m}c_{\pi}x_1^{r_1}\cdots x_m^{r_m}=m!\,[y^m]\,\exp\left[\sum_{k=1}^{m}\frac{x_k}{k}y^k\right]. 
 m!\sum_{r_1+2r_2+\cdots+mr_m=m}\prod_{k=1}^{m}\frac{x_k^{r_k}}{r_k!\cdot k^{r_k}}. 
 m!\prod_{k=1}^{m}\left(\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\frac{x_k^r}{r!\,k^r}y^{kr}\right)=m!\prod_{k=1}^{m}\left(\sum_{r=0}^{\infty}\frac{\left(\frac{x_k y^k}{k}\right)^r}{r!}\right)=m!\prod_{k=1}^{m}\exp\left[\frac{x_k y^k}{k}\right]. 
